is called spotdl

it is a python app that needs youtube music  it pairs the spotify songs with youtube songs 

to install use pip

spotDL can be installed by running pip install spotdl.
On some systems you might have to change pip to pip3.

you may want to use sudo even if it is not recommended
you may also be prompted to install additional packages. install them 

finally to run it use spotdl 

if it does not work you may want to use sudo

sudo spotdl http://spotifysongorplaylist_link

you can also process entire playlist instead of one single song 